author: @purplemoon3831
text:
Darl+ing is a MASTERPIECE. The vocals, the choreo, their outfits, even the background everything is aesthetic 💕💕 I don't have a bias anymore, they're all wrecking my list so hard. 
I'm here simping after Shua's soft and fluffy hair, Cheol's mesmerizing gaze, Dino's smile, Hao's soft voice and visuals, Woozi with his Ruby mic, Vernon starting the song and waving😭, Hoshi's tiger-power dance break and then Kwan emerging behind him, Dokyeom literally being ear candy, Mingyu's perm, Jeonghan's eye smile, Jun being cute and elegant at the same time. Wonwoo's voice is so comforting, I'm glad no one else is covering his lines.


Also it might seem silly but the spelling 'Sukkiri' is so similar to my name, Sukirti, I literally got a mini heartattack reading that. I'm always gonna giggle whenever I read that title🙈😅💖
